title: Reebok Men's Bb4500 Hi 2 Sneaker
description: Reebok Men's Royal Bb4500 Hi2 Sneaker helps you show your respect for the game while keeping classic, everyday style on point. These mid-cut, basketball-inspired men's shoes are sure to be an instant favorite, with a blended leather and mesh upper weighing in for heritage comfort. Plus, a removable sockliner helps keep feet happy all day long.
